name: First A320neo in Calgary! VivaAerobús A320-271N [XA-VIV] Landing and Takeoff at Calgary Airport
description:
When VivaAerobus started service here back in December, I was hopeful that they'd send an A320neo eventually. The chance seemed pretty low, given that they have around 20 A320ceos and only 2 neos, but here it is! The 737MAX is already here at least 2-3 times a day from both WestJet and AC, so the neo was a great surprise! Hope you enjoy what is also my first ever catch of a A320neo!

Thanks for watching!
